books.name: Multiplatform game development in C#
books.description: This hands-on beginners guide gets you building games fast, all with the awesome Unity engine!
review: This book presents an excellent introduction to Unity and C# scripting.
Joe has done an amazing job putting together a book that's detailed, easy to understand, and beginner friendly.
The author takes the reader on a journey through the Unity environment by presenting sample projects in each chapter.
